      <title>纽约市称德克萨斯州州长逃避限制移民巴士的命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/nyc-says-texas-governor-is-skirting-order-limiting-migrant-buses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市官员指责德克萨斯州州长格雷格·阿博特故意规避市长埃里克·亚当斯限制移民巴士抵达的行政命令，称州长是“试图破坏城市稳定”的恶霸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/nyc-says-texas-governor-is-skirting-order-limiting-migrant-buses</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 19:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
