      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/ethiopia-deal-with-renegade-region-spurs-somalia-to-recall-envoy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在埃塞俄比亚这个内陆邻国与脱离飞地索马里兰签署谅解备忘录、允许其进入红海后，索马里召回了驻埃塞俄比亚的特使。]]></description>
